<div id="content" lang="en" dir="ltr">
This skill is a sub-skill of the Combat skill.  It generates a field around the character within which magic cannot work. As such, it can be very useful to prevent monsters from casting offensive spells against you or from teleporting away from you just before you kill them - but it will also prevent you from casting spells, or teleporting away when they've almost killed you! It also inhibits your ability to do magic, affecting *all* the magic and spirituality sub-skills. <p>
This skill does not affect your ability to use scrolls and potions, but other items that require <a class="interwiki" title="Self" href="./Documentation/Skills/Magic-Device"><img src="./wiki/starshine/img/moin-inter.png" alt="[Self]" height="16" width="16">Magic-Device</a> are affected.  At higher levels you gain the ability to detect traps and disrupt all teleportation. 
</p>
